'''2011年泰國水災'''是2011年7月底在[[泰國|泰國]]南部地區因持續暴雨而引發的[[洪災|洪災]]，某些地區的[[降雨量|降雨量]]達120厘米（47英寸）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/IOTD/view.php?id=49929|title=Unseasonal Heavy Rain Floods Thailand|publisher=NASA Earth Observatory|date=2011-04-02|accessdate=2011-04-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205432/http://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/IOTD/view.php?id=49929|dead-url=no}}</ref>，至少已造成366人死亡，兩百萬人受洪水影響<ref>http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/local/230321/recovery-begins-as-rains-ease</ref>。洪水預計將對年產值1000億[[泰銖|泰銖]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Reuters|first=Sun2Surf|title=Severe flooding to reduce Thai shrimp output|url=http://www.thesundaily.com/article.cfm?id=59521|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=The Sun Daily|date=2011-04-01}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>的[[泰國蝦|泰國蝦]]出口帶來衝擊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/01/thailand-floods-shrimp-idUSSGE73001O20110401|title=Severe flooding to reduce Thai shrimp output|publisher=Reuters|date=2011-04-01|accessdate=2011-04-01|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822091620/https://www.reuters.com/article/thailand-floods-shrimp/severe-flooding-to-reduce-thai-shrimp-output-idUSSGE73001O20110401|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[泰國行政區劃|泰國76個府]]中有50個府受到洪水影響<ref name="NZherald">{{cite news|last=AF  P|first=NZHerald|title=Tourists stranded as Thai flood death toll passes 120|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/travellers-tips/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501193&objectid=10716357|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=2011-04-01|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310011502/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/travellers-tips/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501193&objectid=10716357|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中[[洛坤府|洛坤府]]災情最為嚴重，鄰近地區也宣布進入[[緊急狀態|緊急狀態]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/home/Floods-of-fury-30152267.html|title=Floods of fury|accessdate=2011-04-06|date=2011-04-01|publisher=The Nation|quote=Rescue efforts underway to save survivors of destroyed Krabi village....|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607230837/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/home/Floods-of-fury-30152267.html|archivedate=2011-06-07}}</ref>。受災土地面積達160,000公頃（400,000英畝），泰國2011年[[糙米|糙米]]產量恐減少350萬噸<ref name="Berna">{{cite news|last=Muhammad|first=Jamaluddin|title=Death Toll in Thailand Floods Reaches 41|url=http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v5/newsgeneral.php?id=575944|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=Bernama - Malaysian National News Agency|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221202/http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v5/newsgeneral.php?id=575944|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迄今至少5000戶平民和數百名遊客被疏散<ref>{{cite news|last=Online News|first=MCOT|title=Thailand's flood death toll reaches 40|url=http://www.mcot.net/cfcustom/cache_page/190285.html|accessdate=2011-04-03|newspaper=MCOT.NET|date=2011-04-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407083015/http://www.mcot.net/cfcustom/cache_page/190285.html|archivedate=2011-04-07}}</ref>。當局下令關閉共逾200間工廠，並疏散約2萬工人。[[泰國央行|泰國央行]]及政府預期水災將導致1000億[[泰銖|泰銖]]損失，佔全國國內生產總值(GDP)逾1%。泰國政府預估這次重建經費將達33億美元。

[[曼谷|曼谷]]防洪系統見效，多管齊下迅速排洪，首都曼谷避過一劫，災情嚴重的[[大城府|大城府]]共5個大型工業園區遭洪水泛濫，近20萬名工人受影響。泰國財政部已把本年[[GDP|GDP]]增長預期從4%調低至3.7%。[[硬碟|硬碟]]大廠[[威騰電子|威騰]]（[[Western_Digital|Western Digital]]）表示泰國水災對該公司營運和本季供貨予客戶的能力造成「重大影響」（硬碟價格上漲近一倍）。[[東芝|東芝]]（Toshiba）關閉1座硬碟廠，[[日立製作所|日立]]（Hitachi）兩座未遭洪水侵襲的廠房則宣布減產。[[摩根大通|摩根大通]]估計，以泰國為東南亞生產基地的[[日本|日本]]車廠也損失估計逾5億美元，[[丰田汽车|豐田]]及[[本田|本田]]車廠受創最深，淹掉本田全球產量的4.7%<ref>[http://n.yam.com/ebcnews/society/201110/20111018633253.html 泰國重建路遙遙]</ref>。由於洪水淹沒建築物及農田等設施，造成重大經濟損失，被形容為「慢海嘯」。

10月底，水災災情惡化，洪水湧入[[曼谷|曼谷]]北部，內閣召開會議後決定，包括曼谷在內的21個重災區從27日至31日連放5天假，以便民眾躲避水災。

